== Participation at Indonesian team ==
* 3 times at [[Thomas Cup]] (2014, 2016, 2018)
* 1 times at [[Sudirman Cup]] (2015)
* 2 times at Badminton Asia Team Championships (2016, 2018)
* 2 times at SEA Games (2015, 2017)

